---
<Base
  title="EM Music Produções - Prod. Eder Machado"
  description="Grave, masterize, aprenda produção musical ou pegue loops prontos. Fale direto com o Eder Machado."
  redeAtual="EM Music Produções"
>
  <SiteNav whatsappUrl={WHATSAPP_URL} />

  <main>
    <!-- HERO estilo Kronoxx: fundo em movimento (video real quando existir, ou onda
         animada leve como base/fallback), tipografia gigante em cima -->
    <section id="topo" class="relative flex min-h-[100svh] flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden px-6 py-24">
      <div class="absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
        {hasHeroVideo && (
          <video
            class="h-full w-full object-cover opacity-50"
            autoplay
            muted
            loop
            playsinline
            preload="none"
            poster="/images/em-music-logo.png"
          >
            <source src="/videos/hero-bg.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
        )}
        <div class:list={["hero-wave-bg", { "hero-wave-bg--dim": hasHeroVideo }]}>
          {Array.from({ length: 40 }).map((_, i) => {
            const height = 25 + Math.abs(Math.sin(i * 1.7)) * 70;
            const delay = (i % 9) * -0.15;
            return <span class="hero-wave-bar" style={`height:${height.toFixed(0)}%;animation-delay:${delay}s`}></span>;
          })}
        </div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-ink/40 via-ink/70 to-ink"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-ink/30"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <p class="font-body text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brand-pink">
          Chegou pelo adesivo do carro?
        </p>
        <h1 class="balance mt-5 font-display text-6xl leading-[0.92] text-paper sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl">
          BORA FAZER
          <br />
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-pink to-brand-purple bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            MÚSICA DE VERDADE
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-md text-lg text-paper/70">
          Grava, masteriza, aprende ou compra loop pronto. Escolhe o caminho aí embaixo.
        </p>

        <a
          href={WHATSAPP_URL}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-purple to-brand-pink px-8 py-4 font-display text-lg uppercase tracking-wide text-paper"
        >
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-5 w-5 fill-paper"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-8.6 15.1L2 22l5.1-1.3A10 10 0 1 0 12 2Zm0 18.2a8.1 8.1 0 0 1-4.2-1.2l-.3-.2-3 .8.8-2.9-.2-.3A8.2 8.2 0 1 1 12 20.2Zm4.5-6.1c-.2-.1-1.4-.7-1.7-.8s-.4-.1-.6.1-.7.8-.9 1-.3.2-.6 0a6.7 6.7 0 0 1-2-1.2 7.4 7.4 0 0 1-1.4-1.7c-.1-.2 0-.4.1-.5s.2-.3.4-.4a1.6 1.6 0 0 0 .2-.4.5.5 0 0 0 0-.4c0-.1-.6-1.5-.8-2s-.4-.4-.6-.4h-.5a1 1 0 0 0-.7.3 2.9 2.9 0 0 0-.9 2.2 5.1 5.1 0 0 0 1.1 2.7 11.6 11.6 0 0 0 4.4 3.9c.6.3 1.1.4 1.5.5a3.6 3.6 0 0 0 1.6.1 2.7 2.7 0 0 0 1.8-1.2 2.1 2.1 0 0 0 .1-1.2c-.1-.1-.2-.2-.5-.3Z"/></svg>
          Falar com o Eder agora
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-paper/40">Fale direto com o Produtor Eder Machado</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-paper/50">
          Loops e instrumentos dele já tocaram em produções da Netflix, do SBT e no hit
          "Zona de Perigo" (Léo Santana)
        </p>

        <div class="mx-auto mt-14 flex justify-center">
          <span class="scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-5 w-5 fill-paper/40"><path d="M12 16.5 4.5 9l1.4-1.4L12 13.7l6.1-6.1L19.5 9z" /></svg>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FORK: os dois mundos -->
    <section class="px-6 pb-4">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-4xl gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <a
          href="#em-music"
          class="reveal glow-card group rounded-2xl border border-ink-line bg-ink-raised p-6"
        >
          <p class="font-display text-2xl text-brand-pink">EM MUSIC PRODUÇÕES</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-paper/60">
            Piseiro, arrocha, pagode, axé: o que toca na night.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a
          href="#prod-eder"
          class="reveal glow-card group rounded-2xl border border-ink-line bg-ink-raised p-6"
        >
          <p class="font-display text-2xl text-brand-purple">PROD. EDER MACHADO</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-paper/60">
            Produção musical gospel, do jeito que edifica.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- OS 4 CAMINHOS -->
    <section id="em-music" class="px-6 py-14">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-brand-pink">Serviços</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 font-display text-3xl text-paper sm:text-4xl">O que a gente faz por você</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 h-px w-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-purple to-brand-pink"></div>
        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          {paths.map((p) => (
            <a
              href={p.href}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="reveal glow-card flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-ink-line bg-ink-raised p-6"
            >
              <span class={`text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-${p.accent}`}>
                {p.cta}
              </span>
              <h3 class="mt-3 font-display text-xl text-paper">{p.title}</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-paper/60">{p.body}</p>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="prod-eder" class="sr-only" aria-hidden="true"></section>

    <!-- ÚLTIMOS LANÇAMENTOS -->
    <section id="lancamentos" class="px-6 py-14">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-brand-pink">Discografia</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 font-display text-3xl text-paper sm:text-4xl">Últimos lançamentos</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 h-px w-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-purple to-brand-pink"></div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-paper/60">Ouça direto nas plataformas digitais.</p>

        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          {releases.map((r) => (
            <div class="glow-card flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-ink-line bg-ink-raised">
              <span class="relative block aspect-square w-full overflow-hidden">
                <img
                  src={r.cover}
                  alt={`Capa de ${r.title}`}
                  loading="lazy"
                  class="h-full w-full object-cover"
                />
              </span>
              <div class="p-4">
                <p class="font-display text-lg leading-tight text-paper">{r.title}</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-paper/50">{r.artist}</p>
                <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                  <a
                    href={r.spotify}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    aria-label={`Ouvir ${r.title} no Spotify`}
                    class="flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-ink-line py-1 pl-1 pr-2.5 text-[11px] font-semibold text-paper/70 transition hover:border-brand-pink hover:text-paper"
                  >
                    <img src={PLATFORM_LOGOS.spotify} alt="" class="h-4 w-4" loading="lazy" />
                    Spotify
                  </a>
                  <a
                    href={r.apple}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    aria-label={`Ouvir ${r.title} no Apple Music`}
                    class="flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-ink-line py-1 pl-1 pr-2.5 text-[11px] font-semibold text-paper/70 transition hover:border-brand-pink hover:text-paper"
                  >
                    <img src={PLATFORM_LOGOS.apple} alt="" class="h-4 w-4" loading="lazy" />
                    Apple Music
                  </a>
                  <a
                    href={r.deezer}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    aria-label={`Ouvir ${r.title} no Deezer`}
                    class="flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-ink-line py-1 pl-1 pr-2.5 text-[11px] font-semibold text-paper/70 transition hover:border-brand-purple hover:text-paper"
                  >
                    <img src={PLATFORM_LOGOS.deezer} alt="" class="h-4 w-4" loading="lazy" />
                    Deezer
                  </a>
                  <a
                    href={r.youtube}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    aria-label={`Assistir ${r.title} no YouTube`}
                    class="flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-ink-line py-1 pl-1 pr-2.5 text-[11px] font-semibold text-paper/70 transition hover:border-brand-purple hover:text-paper"
                  >
                    <img src={PLATFORM_LOGOS.youtube} alt="" class="h-4 w-4" loading="lazy" />
                    YouTube
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CLIPES REAIS -->
    <section id="videos" class="py-14">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-brand-purple">Portfólio</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 font-display text-3xl text-paper sm:text-4xl">Clipes e produções reais</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 h-px w-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-purple to-brand-pink"></div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-paper/60">Direto dos nossos canais, sem imagem de banco.</p>

        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          {videos.map((v) => (
            <a
              href={v.url}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="glow-card group relative block overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-ink-line bg-ink-raised"
            >
              <span class="relative block aspect-video w-full overflow-hidden">
                <img
                  src={v.thumb}
                  alt={v.title}
                  loading="lazy"
